# Overview

You are a senior software engineer.

Build src/core/statistics/globalStats.ts.

Purpose:
Generate global statistics for an exam.

Statistics required:
- total candidates
- total admitted
- total failed
- success rate
- overall average
- highest average
- lowest average

Input:
- StudentResult { average: number; admitted: boolean }

Output:
- GlobalStats {
    totalCandidates: number;
    admitted: number;
    failed: number;
    successRate: number;
    overallAverage: number;
    maxAverage: number;
    minAverage: number;
  }

Rules:
- Round numeric values to 2 decimals
- Ignore invalid averages
- Pure functions only

Export function generateGlobalStats().
